'''薩拉米香腸戰術'''（Salami tactics），亦稱'''切香腸戰術'''、'''漸進戰術'''，是一種以結盟、威脅來[[分而治之|分化、征服]]的政治和軍事手段。成功運用此戰術，進攻方會以分化敵方、逐漸佔領少數領地的方法，達成統治一大片地區的目的。

==歷史==
“薩拉米香腸戰術”一詞最早出自[[匈牙利語|匈牙利語]]“{{lang|hu|szalámitaktika}}”，它於1940年代末期由匈牙利政治家[[拉科西·馬加什|拉科西·馬加什]]提出、用來描述[[匈牙利共產黨|匈牙利共產黨]]的戰略。<ref>Bullock, Alan, edited by Alan Bullock and Oliver Stallybrass [http://books.google.com/books?id=lWVmAAAAMAAJ The Harper dictionary of modern thought] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=lWVmAAAAMAAJ |date=20200603103720 }}, Harper & Row, 1977.</ref><ref name="Time" /> 當時拉科西的意思是說他已像切[[薩拉米香腸|薩拉米香腸]]一樣將非共產黨逐步分化、消滅。<ref name="Time">Time Magazine. [http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,857130,00.html "Hungary: Salami Tactics"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,857130,00.html |date=20081201074943 }} ''[[Time_Magazine|Time Magazine]]'' (April 14, 1952). Retrieved March 15, 2011</ref><ref name="Time" /><ref>Safire, William, [http://books.google.com/books?id=jK-0NPoMiYoC Safire's Political Dictionary] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=jK-0NPoMiYoC |date=20200607044752 }}, Oxford University Press, 2008 (revised), p.639, ISBN 0-19-534334-4, ISBN 978-0-19-534334-2.</ref>

[[納粹黨|納粹黨]]也曾使用類似的術語，即“Salamitaktik”，但納粹更常用的是[[一體化_(納粹術語)|一體化]]（Gleichschaltung），用以形容納粹黨在1933年奪得德國政權的過程。[[希特勒|希特勒]]也是在執政過程中逐步消滅敵人而最終掌握大權的。<ref>William Shirer, ''[[The_Rise_and_Fall_of_the_Third_Reich|The Rise and Fall of the Third Reich]]''. Touchstone Edition, Simon & Schuster, New York (1990)</ref><ref>Evelin Gerda Lindner, [http://www.humiliationstudies.org/documents/evelin/HumiliationandReactionstoHitlerSocialAlternatives.pdf "Humiliation and Reactions to Hitler’s Seductiveness in Post-War Germany: Personal Reflections"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.humiliationstudies.org/documents/evelin/HumiliationandReactionstoHitlerSocialAlternatives.pdf |date=20101123191812 }} (PDF) Human Dignity and Humiliation Studies. Retrieved March 15, 2011</ref>

